paper_title: Classification of tight contact structures on some Seifert fibered manifolds: I
abstract: We classify tight contact structures with zero Giroux torsion on some Seifert fibered manifolds with four exceptional fibers, $M=M(0;-q_1/p_1,-q_2/p_2,-q_3/p_3,-q_4/p_4)$ where $e_0\leq -4$ and $p_i, q_i \in \mathbb{Z}$ s.t., $p_i\geq 2$, $q_i\geq 1$. We get lower bound by constructing contact structures by Legendrian surgery. We use convex surface theory to obtain the upper bound.
